Copyright 2026 Lightweb Inc. (https://lightweb.net)

=========================================================================

This software is a small standalone daemon that periodically emits BRC-137
ShardManifest datagrams to the IPv6 multicast beacon group, advertising the
local participant's shard_bits configuration and the set of shard groups it
has joined. It is intended for use alongside `bitcoin-shard-proxy`,
`bitcoin-shard-listener`, and `bitcoin-retry-endpoint` to give operators
on-network visibility into the sharding configuration of every participant
and a hook for future automated coordination.

